<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Studix – Parolni tiklash</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0f;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#0a0a0f;min-height:100vh;padding:40px 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px;width:100%;">

          <!-- LOGO HEADER -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding-bottom:32px;text-align:center;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="display:inline-table;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6ee7f7,#a78bfa);border-radius:14px;padding:10px 18px;">
                    <span style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#0a0a0f;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">Studix</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- MAIN CARD -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#13131a;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid #1e1e2e;overflow:hidden;">

              <!-- TOP ACCENT BAR -->
              <tr>
                <td style="height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#a78bfa,#f472b6,#fb923c);"></td>
              </tr>

              <!-- CONTENT -->
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:48px 48px 40px;">

                  <!-- LOCK ICON -->
                  <div style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(167,139,250,0.15),rgba(244,114,182,0.15));border:1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.25);margin-bottom:28px;text-align:center;line-height:64px;">
                    <span style="font-size:28px;">🔐</span>
                  </div>

                  <!-- HEADING -->
                  <h1 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#f0f0ff;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">
                    Parolni tiklash
                  </h1>
                  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.6;">
                    Salom, <span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:500;">{{fullName}}</span>!
                  </p>
                  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 36px;line-height:1.6;">
                    Studix hisobingiz uchun parolni tiklash so'rovi qabul qilindi. Quyidagi tugmani bosib yangi parol o'rnating.
                  </p>

                  <!-- TIMER BADGE -->
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:28px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background:rgba(251,146,60,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:8px 16px;">
                        <span style="font-size:13px;color:#fb923c;font-weight:500;">⏱ Havola 15 daqiqa davomida amal qiladi</span>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- CTA BUTTON -->
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:36px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#f472b6);border-radius:14px;padding:1px;">
                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#f472b6);border-radius:13px;padding:16px 40px;text-align:center;">
                              <a href="{{resetLink}}" style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.2px;">
                                Parolni tiklash →
                              </a>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- DIVIDER -->
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#1e1e2e,transparent);"></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- FALLBACK LINK -->
                  <p style="font-size:12px;color:#4b5563;margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.5;">
                    Tugma ishlamasa, quyidagi havolani brauzeringizga ko'chiring:
                  </p>
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background:#0d0d14;border:1px solid #1e1e2e;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;word-break:break-all;">
                        <a href="{{resetLink}}" style="font-size:12px;color:#6ee7f7;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;">{{resetLink}}</a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- SECURITY NOTE -->
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top:28px;background:rgba(244,114,182,0.06);border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(244,114,182,0.15);">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
                        <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.6;">
                          🛡️ &nbsp;Agar siz bu so'rovni yubormagan bo'lsangiz, ushbu xatni e'tiborsiz qoldiring. Hisobingiz xavfsiz.
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                </td>
              </tr>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- FOOTER -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:28px 0 0;text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#374151;">
                Bu xat <strong style="color:#a78bfa;">Studix</strong> tizimi tomonidan avtomatik yuborildi.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#374151;">
                © 2025 Studix. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
